### Create user

POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "cristopher",
  "email": "cristopher@example.com",
  "password": "testpassword"
}


### Create discussion post

POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/stock/AAPL/discussion
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": 1,
  "body": "Apple looks strong long term.",
  "stance": "bullish"
}


### Get discussion posts

GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/stock/AAPL/discussion


### Get stock details

GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/stock/AAPL